metadata.title: Aspect (1:250,000) - Southcentral
metadata.description: Data Type: Elevation; This layer includes aspect data covering South Central Alaska, organized by 1:250,000 scale USGS quadrangles, and derived from digital elevation model (DEM) data at 1:250,000 scale. The data include both aspect in degrees (0- 360) and in 9 categories. Related data include 1:63,360 scale aspect and elevation data files.
